import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { HistoryList } from './HistoryList' import { useDispatch, useSelector, shallowEqual } from 'react-redux' import { actions } from './redux/AccountRedux' import { ComputerModel, HistoryModel } from 'app/modules/history/models/Account' import { RootState } from 'setup' import { ComputerList } from './ComputerList' import { StaticList } from './StaticList' const AccountPage: React.FC = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch() const histories: HistoryModel[] = useSelector(({ histories }) => histories.histories, shallowEqual) as HistoryModel[] || [] const computers: ComputerModel[] = useSelector(({ histories }) => histories.computers, shallowEqual) as ComputerModel[] || [] useEffect(() => { dispatch(actions.requestHistories(1)) dispatch(actions.requestComputers()) }, []) return ( <>
) } export default AccountPage
